                     <interp inst="t18000528-111-verdict643" type="verdictSubcategory" value="lesserOffence"></interp>
               Of stealing, but not privately
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>
                  <rs id="t18000528-111-punish644" type="punishmentDescription">
